casebody.data:
SAN DIEGANS FOR OPEN GOVERNMENT
v.
SAN DIEGO STATE UNIVERSITY RESEARCH FOUNDATION (INVESTIGATIVE NEWSOURCE) S242529 Supreme Court of California August 16, 2017 Votes: Cantil-Sakauye, C.J., Werdegar, Chin, Liu, Cuéllar and Kruger, JJ.

The petition for review is granted. Further action is deferred pending consideration and disposition of a related issue in Wilson v. Cable News Network, Inc., S239686. Submission of additional briefing pursuant to California Rules of Court, rule 8.520, is deferred pending further order of this court.

**645Corrigan, J., was absent and did not participate.
